<lb n="0781a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0781a18" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1182 [No. 1181, cf. No. 1191]</head>
<lb n="0781a19" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0781010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】承德元年寫東寺三密藏本</note>曼殊<note n="0781011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">室＝師【甲】</note><app n="0781011"><lem wit="【大】">室</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">師</rdg></app>利菩薩&CB00057;藏中一字&CB00057;
<lb n="0781a20" ed="T"/>王經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0781a21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0781a22" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0781012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大）＋唐【元】</note><app n="0781012"><lem wit="【大】">唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">大唐</rdg></app>三藏法師義淨奉　制<note n="0781013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（第二）＋譯【元】</note><app n="0781013"><lem wit="【大】">譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">第二譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0781a23" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT20p0781a2301">爾時釋迦牟尼佛。在淨居天<note n="0781014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔上於天〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781014"><lem wit="【大】">上。於天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>眾中跏
<lb n="0781a24" ed="T"/>趺正念。普觀大眾而告之曰。汝諸天子。當至
<lb n="0781a25" ed="T"/>心聽曼殊室利童子微妙之行。所謂壇場神
<lb n="0781a26" ed="T"/>&CB00057;作法。所須療病護身。第一祕密最上&CB00057;
<lb n="0781a27" ed="T"/>心。一切如來所共宣說咸皆稱歎。是大&CB00057;王。
<lb n="0781a28" ed="T"/>若有善男子善女人。能誦此&CB00057;者。則為受持
<lb n="0781a29" ed="T"/>一切神&CB00057;。汝諸天眾。此大&CB00057;王無能違者。假
<pb n="0781b" id="T20.1182.0781b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0781b01" ed="T"/>使曼殊室利童子菩薩摩訶薩。此&CB00057;亦能隨
<lb n="0781b02" ed="T"/>心自在引攝將來。令使現前為作眾事。況復
<lb n="0781b03" ed="T"/>諸餘菩薩。世出世間所有神&CB00057;。一切障礙悉
<lb n="0781b04" ed="T"/>皆<note n="0781015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔除〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781015"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>遣。有大勇猛有大威力。神驗第一。諸
<lb n="0781b05" ed="T"/>&CB00057;中上一字中尊。此之一字悉能成就一切
<lb n="0781b06" ed="T"/>事業。悉能圓滿所有善法。常在一切世出世
<lb n="0781b07" ed="T"/>間。&CB00057;術之上不可毀壞。是一切佛心。悉能滿
<lb n="0781b08" ed="T"/>足所有求願。汝諸天眾。咸皆一心聽此不可
<lb n="0781b09" ed="T"/>思議具大威力最上神&CB00057;。即說&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0781b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0781b1001" type="dharani"><note n="0781016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵上三本俱有梵字</note>唵叱洛呬焰<note place="inline">此有四字總成一字是故梵漢二體俱<note n="0781017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">存＝在之【甲】</note><app n="0781017"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">在之</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0781b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0781b1101">汝等天眾。此是一切祕密中勝一字&CB00057;王。一
<lb n="0781b12" ed="T"/>切有情無敢違者。一切鬼神不敢親近。一切
<lb n="0781b13" ed="T"/>諸<note n="0781018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781018"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>為吉祥事。一切&CB00057;中最能成立隨意所
<lb n="0781b14" ed="T"/>為。一切世間作大尊勝。於求財者有大自在
<lb n="0781b15" ed="T"/>能令富盛。諸瞋恚中此<note n="0781019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝念【甲】</note><app n="0781019"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">念</rdg></app>慈善。於諸含識
<lb n="0781b16" ed="T"/>悲愍為性。有違逆者皆悉順從。要<note n="0781020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔而〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781020"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>言之。
<lb n="0781b17" ed="T"/>凡有所為悉皆成就。縱不作法入壇場等直
<lb n="0781b18" ed="T"/>爾誦持。手觸彼時即便隨意。&CB00057;衣著時。人皆
<lb n="0781b19" ed="T"/>愛樂見者歡喜若&CB00057;齒木用揩齒時。齒<note n="0781021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔疼〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781021"><lem wit="【大】">疼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>即
<lb n="0781b20" ed="T"/><note n="0781022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝瘥【宋】＊，著【甲】＊</note><note n="0781022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝瘥【宋】＊，＝著【甲】＊</note><app n="0781022"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>。若患眼時。取先陀婆鹽研之為<note n="0781023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">末＝粖【宋】【元】，&CB00331;【甲】</note><note n="0781023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">末＝粖【宋】【元】，＝&CB00331;【甲】</note><app n="0781023"><lem wit="【大】">末</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">粖</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00331;</rdg></app>。&CB00057;七
<lb n="0781b21" ed="T"/>遍已少置眼中。其痛便止。若患耳者。取象馬
<lb n="0781b22" ed="T"/>糞聚上地<note n="0781024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">菌＝園【甲】</note><app n="0781024"><lem wit="【大】">菌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">園</rdg></app>。并<note n="0781025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">苣&CB01091;＝巨勝【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0781025"><lem wit="【大】">苣&CB01091;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【甲】">巨勝</rdg></app>油先陀婆鹽。各取少
<lb n="0781b23" ed="T"/>許&CB00057;之七遍。一處研使碎絞取汁煖之。<note n="0781026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">渧＝滴【三】</note><note n="0781026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">渧＝滴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781026"><lem wit="【大】">渧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">滴</rdg></app>耳
<lb n="0781b24" ed="T"/>孔中其痛便止。若有女人。將產之時。被胎所
<lb n="0781b25" ed="T"/>惱腹中結痛不能疾出。取阿吒留灑根或牛
<lb n="0781b26" ed="T"/>膝根。取無蟲水磨擣令碎。&CB00057;之七遍塗在臍
<lb n="0781b27" ed="T"/>下。即能易出。若人被射。箭鏃入身不能出者。
<lb n="0781b28" ed="T"/>可取<note n="0781027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陳酥＝練蘇【甲】</note><app n="0781027"><lem wit="【大】">陳酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">練蘇</rdg></app>&CB00057;一百八遍。令彼飲之其鏃便出。
<lb n="0781b29" ed="T"/>若患宿食不消。腹中結痛<note n="0781028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（&CB00057;）＋上【甲】</note><app n="0781028"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00057;上</rdg></app>變下瀉<note n="0781029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03659;＝霍【三】</note><note n="0781029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03659;＝霍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781029"><lem wit="【大】">&CB03659;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">霍</rdg></app>亂
<pb n="0781c" id="T20.1182.0781c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0781c01" ed="T"/>畏死者。可取烏鹽或先陀婆鹽或諸雜鹽類。
<lb n="0781c02" ed="T"/>&CB00057;之七遍。研<note n="0781030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔碎〕－【甲】</note><app n="0781030"><lem wit="【大】">碎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>煖水令服便<app source="0781022" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>。或復苦痢
<lb n="0781c03" ed="T"/>不能斷者。取橘柚根及榠樝根。磨擣&CB00057;之七
<lb n="0781c04" ed="T"/>遍。和水服之即<app source="0781022" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0781c05" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0781c0501">若<note n="0781031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＝有【明】</note><app n="0781031"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">有</rdg></app>石女無產生法。欲求男女者。應取阿說
<lb n="0781c06" ed="T"/>健陀根。以<note n="0781032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">酥＝蘇【甲】＊</note><app n="0781032"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>熟煎<note n="0781033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">擣＝禱【甲】</note><app n="0781033"><lem wit="【大】">擣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">禱</rdg></app>之令碎。和黃牛乳&CB00057;
<lb n="0781c07" ed="T"/>二十五遍。待彼女人身淨之時令飲其藥。<note n="0781034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妻＝毒【甲】</note><app n="0781034"><lem wit="【大】">妻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">毒</rdg></app>
<lb n="0781c08" ed="T"/>莫犯他男。夫莫犯他女。未久之間即便有娠。
<lb n="0781c09" ed="T"/>或復女人斷緒無子。<note n="0781035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＝住【甲】</note><app n="0781035"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">住</rdg></app>三五年或復多年。或
<lb n="0781c10" ed="T"/>被他<note n="0781036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">禁＝梵【甲】</note><app n="0781036"><lem wit="【大】">禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">梵</rdg></app>&CB00057;或由<note n="0781037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">厭＝&CB01679;【三】</note><note n="0781037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">厭＝&CB01679;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781037"><lem wit="【大】">厭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB01679;</rdg></app>禱。或因諸病或他所惱
<lb n="0781c11" ed="T"/>或遭毒藥。遇此惡緣遂無子息者。應取少許
<lb n="0781c12" ed="T"/>孔雀尾。安<note n="0781038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陳＝練【甲】</note><app n="0781038"><lem wit="【大】">陳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">練</rdg></app><app source="0781032" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>中箭之數沸。研令相得。投
<lb n="0781c13" ed="T"/>少石蜜量如<note n="0781039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">棗＝朿【甲】</note><app n="0781039"><lem wit="【大】">棗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">朿</rdg></app>許。&CB00057;二<note n="0781040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十＋（二十）【甲】</note><app n="0781040"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">十二十</rdg></app>七遍服之令盡。
<lb n="0781c14" ed="T"/>於後七日中日日常以石蜜和乳。每&CB00057;七遍
<lb n="0781c15" ed="T"/>飲之。女身清淨諸病皆<note n="0781041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝瘥【宋】＊</note><app n="0781041"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>即便有娠。若有女
<lb n="0781c16" ed="T"/>人月水不息。應以阿藍部根或以藍根<note n="0781042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＝或【甲】</note><app n="0781042"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">或</rdg></app>握
<lb n="0781c17" ed="T"/>擣之。和乳熟煎&CB00057;一百八遍服之即<app source="0781041" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若患
<lb n="0781c18" ed="T"/>頭痛者。應以烏羽&CB00057;之七遍。掃<note n="0781043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拂痛＝拂病【三】，&CB01673;痛【甲】</note><note n="0781043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拂痛＝拂病【宋】【元】【明】，＝&CB01673;痛【甲】</note><app n="0781043"><lem wit="【大】">拂痛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">拂病</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB01673;痛</rdg></app>處即便
<lb n="0781c19" ed="T"/>永<app source="0781041" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若人患瘧。或一日二日三日四日發
<lb n="0781c20" ed="T"/>者。或常熱病或暫時熱病。應以乳粥和<app source="0781032" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">蘇</rdg></app>&CB00057;
<lb n="0781c21" ed="T"/>一百八遍。食之即<app source="0781041" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若人被他<note n="0781044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">厭＝&CB01679;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0781044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">厭＝&CB01679;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0781044"><lem wit="【大】">厭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&CB01679;</rdg></app>魅<note n="0781045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蠱＝蟲【三】</note><note n="0781045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠱＝蟲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781045"><lem wit="【大】">蠱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">蟲</rdg></app>毒
<lb n="0781c22" ed="T"/>所中。應作反緣心。&CB00057;自<app><lem wit="【CBETA】">己</lem><rdg wit="【大】">已</rdg></app>面一百八遍。<note n="0781046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觀＝視【甲】</note><app n="0781046"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">視</rdg></app>彼
<lb n="0781c23" ed="T"/>病人所患便<note n="0781047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝瘥【宋】，著【甲】</note><note n="0781047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝瘥【宋】，＝著【甲】</note><app n="0781047"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">著</rdg></app>。若人被邪鬼羯吒布單那等
<lb n="0781c24" ed="T"/>諸鬼所著。或小兒諸病。但是一切非人所為
<pb n="0782a" id="T20.1182.0782a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0782a01" ed="T"/>共相惱者。應&CB00057;自手一百八遍。<note n="0782001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩病＝病摩【甲】</note><app n="0782001"><lem wit="【大】">摩病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">病摩</rdg></app>人頭即
<lb n="0782a02" ed="T"/>眾病皆<app source="0781041" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若人被蛇蠍所蜇或狂狗所傷。以
<lb n="0782a03" ed="T"/>氣急吹瘡上。&CB00057;之七七遍即<app source="0781041" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">瘥</rdg></app>。若有人患癩
<lb n="0782a04" ed="T"/>病瘦病者。應洗浴潔淨於閑靜處。常誦此&CB00057;
<lb n="0782a05" ed="T"/>悉皆除愈。凡誦&CB00057;之人。常須遠離惡人不淨
<lb n="0782a06" ed="T"/>臭穢之處不近酒肉五辛。一心受持無不驗
<lb n="0782a07" ed="T"/>者。若有一日常誦一遍。能護自身。若誦二遍
<lb n="0782a08" ed="T"/>能護同伴。若誦三遍能護一家。若誦四遍能
<lb n="0782a09" ed="T"/>護一村。若誦五遍能護一城。若誦百遍能護
<lb n="0782a10" ed="T"/>一國。若誦千遍能護四天下。以要言之略述
<lb n="0782a11" ed="T"/>如是。療病護身隨時利益。若更有餘所為之
<lb n="0782a12" ed="T"/>事。皆隨意作無不成就。爾時諸天大眾聞佛
<lb n="0782a13" ed="T"/>說此一字&CB00057;王經已。歡喜奉行<note place="inline">若復有人志求解脫<note n="0782002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">希＋（有）【甲】</note><app n="0782002"><lem wit="【大】">希</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">希有</rdg></app>大利益現望
<lb n="0782a14" ed="T"/>果證者當可<note n="0782003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">至＝志【宋】</note><app n="0782003"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">志</rdg></app>心依&CB00057;藏中作大&CB00057;法廣說如經</note>。</p>
<lb n="0782a15" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0782004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0782004"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0782005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（曼殊室利菩薩&CB00057;藏中）＋一【三】</note><note n="0782005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（曼殊室利菩薩&CB00057;藏中）＋一【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0782005"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曼殊室利菩薩&CB00057;藏中一</rdg></app>字&CB00057;王經<note n="0782006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本奧書曰，承德元年丁巳十二月三日書了一交了</note></jhead></juan></div1>
